SUMMARY:What on Earth?!
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Environment Day with a quiz that’s anything but ordinary! \nWhat on Earth?! is a lively\, interactive session designed by Quizmaster Berty Ashley to surprise\, challenge\, and entertain. Expect curious questions\, unexpected twists\, and a playful dive into themes that connect us to the world we live in. Whether you’re a quiz buff or just in it for the fun\, this is your chance to learn something new—and maybe even win a prize or two! \nThis quiz is for teams of two to three people. So\, bring your friends\, bring your curiosity\, and get ready to find out… what on Earth is going on?! \nThis event is a part of the Environment Day programming at BIC. \n  \n
URL:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/event/what-on-earth-2/
LOCATION:Bangalore International Centre\, 7\, 4th Main Road\, Domlur II Stage\, Bangalore\, Karnataka\, 560071\, India
CATEGORIES:Environment,History,Science
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Thumbnail_WOE.jpg
END:VEVENT
