SUMMARY:Daag
DESCRIPTION:Language: Hindi \nBindiya\, a tailor\, wants to lead a lavish life. She stitches clothes for ladies\, aspiring to enter their world. However\, her customers short-change her\, and impose impossible deadlines. How can she afford to climb the social ladder when those on the upper rungs constantly knock her down? Is it inevitable?  \nSupported by: \n \n
URL:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/event/daag/
LOCATION:Bangalore International Centre\, 7\, 4th Main Road\, Domlur II Stage\, Bangalore\, Karnataka\, 560071\, India
CATEGORIES:Performing Arts,Theatre
